# aionowplaying
A cross-platform Now Playing client

## CI Status

![GitHub Workflow Matrix Status](http://github-actions.40ants.com/BruceZhang1993/aionowplaying/matrix.svg)

## Usage
```shell
# Using pip
pip install aionowplaying
# Using poetry
poetry add aionowplaying
```

